    @Mojo(name="property-updates-aggregate-report",
      requiresDependencyResolution=RUNTIME,
      threadSafe=true,
      aggregator=true)
public class PropertyUpdatesAggregateReportMojo
extends AbstractPropertyUpdatesReportMojo
    Generates an aggregate report of available updates for properties of a project which are linked to the dependencies and/or plugins of a project.
    Since:
